#14. Program to find the Compound Interest compounded annually and the total amount when the 
#Principal, Rate of Interest and Time are entered by the user.

p=eval(input("enter principal amount: "))
r=eval(input("enter rate of interest per month: "))
t=eval(input("enter time in month: "))

CI= p*(1+(r/100))**t - p
T=p*(1 + (r/t))**t 
 
print(f''' compound interest is {CI} 
      and total amount is {T}''')
